00:58:23.900 --> 00:58:24.700 align:middle line:90%
>>ARDAGH: Right.

00:58:24.700 --> 00:58:26.580 align:middle line:84%
So I think the first
thing to understand

00:58:26.580 --> 00:58:29.810 align:middle line:84%
is that anger, or
violence anyway,

00:58:29.810 --> 00:58:35.290 align:middle line:84%
is the expression of an
energy gone out of control.

00:58:35.290 --> 00:58:41.860 align:middle line:84%
Anger, as we understand it,
is feeling the energy, right?

00:58:41.860 --> 00:58:46.490 align:middle line:84%
And so whether it's verbal
