00:58:46.490 --> 00:58:48.180 align:middle line:90%
that is usually destructive.

00:58:48.180 --> 00:58:50.890 align:middle line:84%
But the energy itself,
if we reel it back,

00:58:50.890 --> 00:58:54.550 align:middle line:84%
the energy itself is actually
a good thing for a man to have.

00:58:54.550 --> 00:58:58.400 align:middle line:84%
A man who's lost that,
[SLAPPING] [GRUNTING], feeling,

00:58:58.400 --> 00:59:01.075 align:middle line:84%
